# Catface symbol algebra cookbook
# Object symbols: T test, S source, ▣ record, I info, ! TODO, ✓ done, ◯ concept.
# Edge symbols: ✓ verifies, ⊢ supports, ⊣ blocks, ≤ refines, ⇢ id-link, ⊃ contains.

@tests -> reader
reader <- @tests
%verifies @tests -> codegen
@obs -> @dec
@todo -> @source
@blocked <- @todo
@notes reader
@obs reader
@dec syntax
@inf inference
